additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: NOODLES: Wheat flour (contains iron, zinc, vitamins [B2, B1, folic acid]) (70%), palm oil (antioxidants [307b, 320, 321]), tapioca starch, salt, acidity regulators (501, 450, 451), colour (160a), emulsifier (1450), stabiliser (414). SEASONING POWDER: Creamer (glucose, palm fat, sodium caseinate, stabiliser [340], emulsifier [471], anticaking agent [551]), salt, flavour enhancers (621, 635), sugar, flavouring powder, spices (garlic, onion, ginger, pepper), sesame seeds, yeast extract, hydrolysed plant protein (soya, stabiliser [1400]), spring onion, thickener (412). SEASONING PASTE: Palm oil, spices (garlic, onion), sesame oil, flavouring (milk fat, coconut oil), sugar. FRIED GARNISH: Fried shallot chips (shallot, palm oil, wheat flour).

additionalProperty.name: Allergen
additionalProperty.value: Contains Soybean, Contains Wheat, Contains Milk, Contains Sesame Seeds

description: Prepare an authentic Japanese ramen with this premium instant noodle. Convenient yet flavoursome, Nissin Ramen (Kyushu Black) offers the perfect combination of chewy noodles, cloudy soup broth and rich flavours. It is quick and easy to prepare, ideal for a simple instant meal.
name: Ramen Kyushu Black Noodle
